{"id":652412,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2020/08/【图说天朝】苹果一定撑落去-《苹果日报》加/","date":"2020-08-11T00:45:19Z","modified":"2020-08-11T18:29:17Z","title":"【图说天朝】”苹果一定撑落去“ 《苹果日报》加印至55万份","content":"<blockquote class=\"wp-embedded-content\" data-secret=\"sQ4rVoAvDX\"><p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2020/08/%e6%88%90%e6%8a%a5%ef%bd%9c-%e8%a2%ab%e6%8d%95%e4%ba%ba%e5%a3%ab%e5%8f%8a%e6%b6%89%e5%8f%8a%e7%bd%aa%e5%90%8d%ef%bc%88%e9%99%84%e8%a1%a8%e6%a0%bc%ef%bc%89/\">成报｜ 被捕人士及涉及罪名（附表格）</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><iframe class=\"wp-embedded-content\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts\" security=\"restricted\" style=\"position: absolute; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px);\" title=\"《成报｜ 被捕人士及涉及罪名（附表格）》—中国数字时代\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2020/08/%e6%88%90%e6%8a%a5%ef%bd%9c-%e8%a2%ab%e6%8d%95%e4%ba%ba%e5%a3%ab%e5%8f%8a%e6%b6%89%e5%8f%8a%e7%bd%aa%e5%90%8d%ef%bc%88%e9%99%84%e8%a1%a8%e6%a0%bc%ef%bc%89/embed/#?secret=sQ4rVoAvDX\" data-secret=\"sQ4rVoAvDX\" width=\"600\" height=\"338\" frameborder=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\"></iframe></p>\n<blockquote class=\"wp-embedded-content\" data-secret=\"sWDDc7i4kf\"><p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2020/08/bbc-%ef%bd%9c%e9%bb%8e%e6%99%ba%e8%8b%b1%e8%a2%ab%e6%8d%95%e5%90%8e%e5%a3%b9%e4%bc%a0%e5%aa%92%e8%82%a1%e4%bb%b7%e4%b8%a4%e6%97%a5%e6%b6%a8%e8%b6%8510%e5%80%8d-%e9%a6%99%e6%b8%af%e5%b8%82%e6%b0%91/\">BBC ｜黎智英被捕后壹传媒股价两日涨超10倍 香港市民抢购《苹果日报》示支持</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><iframe class=\"wp-embedded-content\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts\" security=\"restricted\" style=\"position: absolute; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px);\" title=\"《BBC ｜黎智英被捕后壹传媒股价两日涨超10倍 香港市民抢购《苹果日报》示支持》—中国数字时代\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2020/08/bbc-%ef%bd%9c%e9%bb%8e%e6%99%ba%e8%8b%b1%e8%a2%ab%e6%8d%95%e5%90%8e%e5%a3%b9%e4%bc%a0%e5%aa%92%e8%82%a1%e4%bb%b7%e4%b8%a4%e6%97%a5%e6%b6%a8%e8%b6%8510%e5%80%8d-%e9%a6%99%e6%b8%af%e5%b8%82%e6%b0%91/embed/#?secret=sWDDc7i4kf\" data-secret=\"sWDDc7i4kf\" width=\"600\" height=\"338\" frameborder=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\"></iframe></p>\n<p>更新：《苹果日报》加印至55万份。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-652422\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/EfGJqfzVAAEfTtJ-150x150.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"279\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/EfGJqfzVAAEfTtJ-300x167.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/EfGJqfzVAAEfTtJ-768x428.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/EfGJqfzVAAEfTtJ.png 803w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>香港壹传媒大楼昨日被警方搜查多个小时。《苹果日报》继续编采工作，印刷部凌晨出版最新一份《苹果日报》，以创办人黎智英被捕为头条，标题为「苹果一定撑落去」。</p>\n<p>《苹果日报》在社交网站表示，两星期前印刷数量是7万多份，今日发行35万份。根据《苹果日报》的网上直播，有市民凌晨在旺角一带的报纸档排队，一度出现人龙。</p>\n<p>黎智英及壹传媒多名高层，昨天被警方拘捕，涉嫌违反《港区国安法》及串谋诈骗等。</p>\n<p>警方出动过百人，到壹传媒大楼蒐证约6小时，期间进入编采部楼层，拉起封锁线，并带走25箱证物。</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-652418\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/IMG_3008-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"667\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/IMG_3008-225x300.jpg 225w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/IMG_3008-768x1024.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/IMG_3008.jpg 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-652413\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/IMG_3013-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"333\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/IMG_3013-300x200.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/IMG_3013-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/IMG_3013-768x512.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/IMG_3013-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/IMG_3013-1080x720.jpg 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/IMG_3013.jpg 1620w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /> <img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-652414\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/IMG_3009-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"281\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/IMG_3009-300x169.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/IMG_3009-1024x576.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/IMG_3009-768x432.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/IMG_3009.jpg 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /> <img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-652415\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/IMG_3010-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"375\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/IMG_3010-300x225.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/IMG_3010-1024x768.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/IMG_3010-768x576.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/IMG_3010.jpg 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /> <img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-652416\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/IMG_3011-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"375\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/IMG_3011-300x225.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/IMG_3011-1024x768.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/IMG_3011-768x576.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/IMG_3011.jpg 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /> <img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-652417\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/IMG_3012-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"375\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/IMG_3012-300x225.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/IMG_3012-1024x768.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/IMG_3012-768x576.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/IMG_3012.jpg 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<div id=\"attachment_652419\" style=\"width: 510px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-652419\" class=\"wp-image-652419\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/w644-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"375\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/w644-300x225.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/w644.jpg 644w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-652419\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">旺角一带的报纸档，一度出现人龙。（关铭辉摄）</p></div>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-652423\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/IMG_3006-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"1083\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/IMG_3006-138x300.jpg 138w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/IMG_3006-473x1024.jpg 473w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/IMG_3006-768x1664.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/IMG_3006-709x1536.jpg 709w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/IMG_3006-945x2048.jpg 945w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/IMG_3006.jpg 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-652438\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/File-11-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"667\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/File-11-225x300.jpg 225w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/File-11-768x1024.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/File-11.jpg 960w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<div id=\"attachment_652491\" style=\"width: 510px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-652491\" class=\"wp-image-652491\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/8.11-香港人排隊撐黎智英次子經營的「四季常餐」-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"321\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/8.11-香港人排隊撐黎智英次子經營的「四季常餐」-300x193.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/8.11-香港人排隊撐黎智英次子經營的「四季常餐」-1024x658.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/8.11-香港人排隊撐黎智英次子經營的「四季常餐」-768x493.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/8.11-香港人排隊撐黎智英次子經營的「四季常餐」-1080x694.jpg 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/8.11-香港人排隊撐黎智英次子經營的「四季常餐」.jpg 1470w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-652491\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">8.11 香港人排隊撐黎智英次子經營的「四季常餐」</p></div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"zh\" dir=\"ltr\">苹果一定要撑下去<br />香港人一定要撑下去<br />大陆人要努力打到共产党</p>\n<p>（香港朋友帮我收藏一张今天的报纸，记住历史。） <a href=\"https://t.co/mc0Pl8rgHR\">pic.twitter.com/mc0Pl8rgHR</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; 华涌 (@HuaYong798) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/HuaYong798/status/1293042009809141762?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">August 11, 2020</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"zh\" dir=\"ltr\">在香港旺角街头的报摊人们在连夜排队买苹果日报，有的一人买十几份。一位民众说这是为了撑苹果日报，撑香港新闻自由。苹果日报办公室所在的壹传媒大楼10日遭警方搜查，壹传媒创办人黎智英涉嫌煽动分裂罪被捕。苹果日报表示工作人员要“坚守岗位，继续以文字守护真相”，并鼓励民众以买报纸撑苹果日报。 <a href=\"https://t.co/aQXB9V1QSJ\">pic.twitter.com/aQXB9V1QSJ</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; 美国之音中文网 (@VOAChinese) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/VOAChinese/status/1292936458890878982?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">August 10, 2020</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"zh\" dir=\"ltr\">【民心不可侮】香港警方昨天抓走黎智英和他的两个儿子，抓了苹果日报4名高管，搜查苹果日报，企图以“执法”声势制造恐惧。但天地有正气，民心不可侮！股市壹传媒股价涨幅一度扩大340%；未被捕副社长决定苹果日报明天照常出街！港人要求苹果日报明天印50万份，香港市民说就是出白纸也会买！天地有正气！ <a href=\"https://t.co/mZaJEMV2E8\">pic.twitter.com/mZaJEMV2E8</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; 韩连潮 (@lianchaohan) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/lianchaohan/status/1292783081703825410?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">August 10, 2020</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"zh\" dir=\"ltr\">（轉）<br />荃灣海濱花園有心人 <a href=\"https://t.co/fpu1yOalNx\">pic.twitter.com/fpu1yOalNx</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; 大浪小濤 (@siutopoon) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/siutopoon/status/1293005240136941570?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">August 11, 2020</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"zh\" dir=\"ltr\">剛才買蘋果日報，店員問「一份？」，我就知道人哋買唔止一份，我問「最多買咗幾份？」，店員答：「五份」🤣 <a href=\"https://t.co/5IYGPwdqtR\">pic.twitter.com/5IYGPwdqtR</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; V神王@三倍光速 (@Wong666V) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/Wong666V/status/1292960089385529344?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">August 10, 2020</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n","author":1052,"categories":[18271,38827,38913,38955],"tags":[28126,10794,41444,38988,21970]}